Set Up Required Minimum Distribution (RMD) Service Process

Your customers can use this service process to raise requests to set up Required Minimum Distribution of their retirement accounts.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Setup and Configuration

Use Service Process Studio to enable the Set Up Required Minimum Distribution service process. This gives agents an easy-to-follow process for capturing customer requests to select payment schedules and payment options.

Submit a Request

Service agents can capture and submit a Set Up Required Minimum Distribution request using the Set Up Required Minimum Distribution OmniScript.
title: Set Up Required Minimum Distribution (RMD) Service Process Guide
